  %title Moped: Driver

%h1 Driver

%p
  The driver is the core of Moped that is used to interact with MongoDB. It is
  based of almost entirely four classes: <code>Session</code>,
  <code>Collection</code>, <code>Indexes</code>, and <code>Query</code>.

